* Summing (inverting) op-amp, 3 inputs
Va ina 0 DC 0.86
Vb inb 0 DC 0.42
Vc inc 0 DC 1.45
Ra ina minus 8.2k
Rb inb minus 8.2k
Rc inc minus 8.2k
Rf out minus 33k
.subckt IDEAL_OPAMP in+ in- out
Rin in+ in- 1000Meg
E1 out 0 in+ in- 1e6
.ends IDEAL_OPAMP

X1 0 minus out IDEAL_OPAMP
.op
.print dc V(out)
.end